name: Distant Drums
comments: After Reeves had died in a plane crash in July 1964, Chet Atkins overdubbed the 1961 Reeves demo with new background music. Released in March 1966 on a RCA Victor single, it became Nr. 1 C&W and Nr. 1 UK. The undubbed demo would later appear on the Bear Family box set "Welcome to My World".
